4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with sought-after skills in JavaScript and Python over 18 weeks. The program consists of three classes per week, with a favorable student-teacher ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is required, and classes are available in English and Spanish. Students will gain hands-on experience by developing a final project, enhancing their web development skills, and learning about algorithms and APIs. Upon completion, graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop